Did something for /Collared/. But looking back, it might fit here more.
What if you were a popular character in the humiesphere?

>Get taken to furry Earth, courtesy of truck-sama.
>One moment a loud horn resonates in your ears, the next you're waking up in a dingy alley.
>It feels like you're going through the worst hangover of your life.
>But considering what just happened, it could be much worse.
>After dealing with the panic from the more-than-near death experience and realization that you're still alive somehow, you get up from the floor.
>You look out of the alley, keeping your head down as you try to get a feel of the land.
>Furries everywhere.
>Just going on with their days, buying stuff, driving about, the usual.
>A few notice your presence and give you a suspicious look.
>Fair, considering you're creeping around a corner.
>After seeing that they haven't ran off screaming, you make your way out of the alley, feeling more courageous.
>Their odd gazes persist. But they leave you be as you consider your situation.
>You haven't seen another human around yet.
>What seems to be this universe's equivalent of a geek store gets your attention.
>Poking around, you take in a bunch of this world's media.
>Pretty cool honestly.
